lyrics:
[Verse]
I dreamt of sunsets, on a golden coast
A place where wild hearts leave a lasting boast
I packed my bags, the journey soon begun
To the rhythm of Ibiza, where it all comes undone

[Chorus]
I'm becoming Ibiza, dancing through the night
Heart pounding with the music, feeling so alive
Lost in the magic, as the beats take control
I'm becoming Ibiza, a part of its soul
